{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2015/05/04/ionic的安装和配置.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e9bfcf45-38d6-5041-abd2-770c489da677","excerpt":"ionic的安装配置的坑 前一阵子react-native很火，甚是嫉妒啊，目前只支持iOS。。。T_T\n不必要一直追求native，（虽然我还是试验了nativescript），在安卓上面还是可以尝试写写hybrid应用。 安装ionic，安装android-sdk-r22（可以用hx.gy:108…","html":"<h1>ionic的安装配置的坑</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>前一阵子react-native很火，甚是嫉妒啊，目前只支持iOS。。。T_T<br>\n不必要一直追求native，（虽然我还是试验了nativescript），在安卓上面还是可以尝试写写hybrid应用。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装ionic，安装android-sdk-r22（可以用hx.gy:1080代理）</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g cordova ionic</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>创建一个空/标签/侧边栏工程</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">ionic start myApp blank/tabs/sidemenu</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>运行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd myApp\nchmod 777 * -R\nionic platform add android\nionic build android\nionic run android</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>用浏览器测试</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">ionic serve</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2015/05/04/ionic的安装和配置.html","date":"May 04, 2015","title":"ionic的安装和配置"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2015/05/04/ionic的安装和配置.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2015/04/12/环渤海之行后感.html","title":"环渤海之行后感"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2015/05/04/nativescript试探报告.html","title":"nativescript试探报告"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}